WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.497 --> 00:00:01.629
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.629 --> 00:00:03.578
Praise the Lord for another day.

00:00:03.578 --> 00:00:06.030
This is day 47, I believe.

00:00:06.699 --> 00:00:18.756
Braden and I are out here at the park to do a video because I wanted to show you that this isn't a green screen; these are real live leaves here in the park.

00:00:18.756 --> 00:00:20.049
It's so beautiful.

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:23.933
I just love nature and what the Lord has done in this fall season.

00:00:24.235 --> 00:00:32.970
I just wanted to say thank you all for all the likes, all the subscribers, and all the support you've shown this channel over the last year.

00:00:32.970 --> 00:00:35.695
It has been amazing to see what the Lord has done.

00:00:35.950 --> 00:00:44.920
My son was telling me about all the people and where you all come from—all the different comments saying you've been watching from all over the world.

00:00:46.662 --> 00:00:49.941
We just want to say thank you for supporting us.

00:00:50.608 --> 00:01:17.787
I was just thinking about the things the Lord is talking to me about regarding the end times and how close we are to the Lord Jesus coming back.

00:01:17.787 --> 00:01:35.640
Looking beyond the next four years, it is going to be a very interesting time frame.

00:01:37.172 --> 00:02:02.340
I try not to be negative, but speaking to my audience right now, I'm telling you there are some trying and very serious days ahead for the body of Christ.

00:02:02.340 --> 00:02:06.267
There will be great persecution.

00:02:06.267 --> 00:02:27.858
I talked to Pastor Steve Cioccolanti on the phone today, and we were going over the time frames and what the Lord has shown both of us.

00:02:42.019 --> 00:02:42.234
We talked about crypto, President Trump, and the things that we see coming.

00:03:02.134 --> 00:03:02.409
It was a very interesting conversation.

00:03:02.409 --> 00:03:07.720
His revelation involves the horses of the apocalypse.

00:03:11.257 --> 00:03:25.502
He believes we went through COVID for three and a half years, and now we have a war cycle for three and a half years.

00:03:25.502 --> 00:03:34.337
After that, we go through pestilence and plague for another three and a half years.

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:55.239
He said on the phone today that the end of 2026, or the summer of 2026, is when he believes we will see a great drought and a great plague.

00:03:55.239 --> 00:04:02.020
That would be the midterm of President Trump's presidency.

00:04:10.866 --> 00:04:18.764
I warned you all that I saw President Trump standing on a platform, addressing the American people and warning them of a major, deadly plague.

00:04:18.764 --> 00:04:25.670
It was a very serious time frame.

00:04:25.670 --> 00:04:35.455
Steve believes the horses of the apocalypse are riding right now.

00:04:35.455 --> 00:04:51.543
He believes that the white horse was the corona and the red horse is riding right now with war.

00:04:51.543 --> 00:05:04.804
He believes a great acceleration of war will be taking place from 2025 through 2026, especially with what we saw with Hamas.

00:05:12.367 --> 00:05:12.800
I weigh out what he's saying in my spirit.

00:05:14.067 --> 00:05:25.686
Some people don't believe the horses are riding yet; they believe that happens during the seven years of tribulation.

00:05:34.528 --> 00:05:34.816
But he believes they ride before the tribulation begins.

00:05:34.816 --> 00:05:57.800
I like to talk to people and listen to what they feel the Holy Spirit is telling them, instead of always saying, 'This is the way it is.

00:05:57.800 --> 00:06:04.420
' I gleaned a lot from the conversation today.

00:06:04.420 --> 00:06:09.372
It stretches me to listen.

00:06:09.372 --> 00:06:19.093
We are in a serious time frame.

00:06:19.093 --> 00:06:35.131
I believe the Lord gave us a four-year window for revival—a major outpouring of the Spirit to bring in the harvest.

00:06:35.131 --> 00:06:43.232
God is giving us an extended amount of grace.

00:06:43.232 --> 00:07:08.439
When the end of that shmita cycle, the end of the Shemitah cycle, occurs and President Trump's presidency is over in 2028, that would end that cycle of the shmita.

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:16.719
I believe the catching away could happen in that time frame.

00:07:16.719 --> 00:07:32.880
I believe we'll have an outpouring of finances, and we're going to see that in the body of Christ.

00:07:32.880 --> 00:07:51.462
I've seen a great economic crisis coming during President Trump's presidency, and I believe we're going to see some different things.

00:07:51.462 --> 00:07:57.709
Things are escalating at a rapid pace.

00:07:57.709 --> 00:08:16.098
Pastor Steve believes we're going to enter into a major season of war in 2025 with Russia, but we're praying against that.

00:08:21.746 --> 00:08:30.620
I'm praying for peace, a major harvest of souls, and an extended four-year window for revival and an outpouring of finances.

00:08:30.620 --> 00:08:42.847
We're going to see an acceleration of the birthing pains that are on us.

00:08:42.847 --> 00:09:02.100
It's not going to be just economic, political, or about a plague; it's going to be signs in the heavens and the earth, like weather with volcanoes and earthquakes.

00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:11.045
We're going to see another side of things that has to do with the environment.

00:09:11.045 --> 00:09:23.857
I saw a great acceleration of environmental events: tsunamis, major hurricanes, and long-track tornadoes.

00:09:23.857 --> 00:09:33.330
But as a believer, you have authority to pray protection and a hedge around your family.

00:09:33.330 --> 00:09:39.640
No weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:49.184
A thousand shall fall at your side, and ten thousand at your right hand, but it will not come nigh you.

00:09:49.184 --> 00:09:55.600
That's why I was telling you to pray for RFK Jr.

00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:08.600
—that God is giving us a window of opportunity for grace and a season of great harvest.

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:15.377
Our prayers in October gave us this window.

00:10:15.377 --> 00:10:29.560
What will we do with this next four years with President Trump coming in and a season of great blessing?

00:10:29.560 --> 00:10:46.640
Even though I saw an acceleration of war and great darkness, we serve the Lord and have blessing on us.

00:10:47.240 --> 00:10:57.406
I believe this will be a season of favor like you've never seen before.

00:10:57.406 --> 00:11:09.040
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm giving favor to My people, a supernatural abundance of favor.

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:16.560
' We are ambassadors of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:21.320
Supernatural favor is coming to you and your family.

00:11:21.320 --> 00:11:42.509
For those who have joined this channel and become part of our family here, I believe that covering and blessing come over you as you help us out.

00:11:42.851 --> 00:11:52.360
We are a body moving and operating together in the favor of God.

00:12:00.147 --> 00:12:00.500
Supernatural abundance is coming to your household.

00:12:00.500 --> 00:12:07.827
The Lord told me last night to start focusing on the dead being raised.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.240
This is part of the Great Commission.

00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:27.280
He told us to raise the dead, cast out devils, and lay hands on the sick.

00:12:27.280 --> 00:12:37.680
We're going to see more of this in these last days.

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:45.800
It's going to take people getting bold in their faith.

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:46.015
Let's pray.

00:12:46.015 --> 00:12:53.320
Father, I thank You for every single person represented here today.

00:13:04.707 --> 00:13:06.455
I thank You that they are healed and whole by the stripes of Jesus.

00:13:06.455 --> 00:13:10.630
We pray for RFK Jr.

00:13:18.950 --> 00:13:26.540
right now, that he will be victorious in every area of his life concerning the health and food administration.

00:13:38.154 --> 00:13:43.780
