00:15:19.383 --> 00:15:35.791
We are the salt, and we are anointed and appointed.

00:15:35.791 --> 00:15:55.960
Even over South Korea, we pray that we will not see a tyrant government trying to lock everybody down.

00:15:57.688 --> 00:16:02.915
We pray that those who need to be removed are removed.

00:16:11.697 --> 00:16:19.935
We see an acceleration of the glory of God even in South Korea, over Asia, China, Japan, the Philippines, Africa, and South America.

00:16:19.935 --> 00:16:28.075
We pray for restoration in marriages and peace in every home.

00:16:28.075 --> 00:16:32.040
In the name of Jesus, Amen.

00:16:32.040 --> 00:16:36.880
Well, everybody, thank you for joining me.

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:44.020
